quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  56,75,Fela uksimu bimevakÄḟÂṀÄḟnnnucumi
  56,76,Ve innehu lekasemun lev taÂṀlemune ÂṀazÄḟymun
  56,77,ÄḞnnehu lekurÂṀanun keriymun
  56,78,Fiy kitamin meknunin
