  56,80,Tenziylun min rabbilÂṀalemiyne
  56,81,Efebihazelhadiysi entum mudhinune
  56,82,Ve tecÂṀalune rizkakum ennekum tukezzibune
  56,83,Felevla iza beleÄatilhulkume
  56,84,Ve entum hÄḟyneizin tenzurune
  56,85,Ve nahnu akrebu ileyhi minkum ve lakin la tubsÄḟrune
  56,86,Felevla in kuntum Äayre mediyniyne
  56,87,TerciÂṀuneha in kuntum sadikÄḟyne
  56,88,Feemma in kane minelmukarrebiyne
  56,89,Feravhun ve reyhanun ve cennetu naÂṀÄḟymin
  56,90,Ve emma in kane min ashabilyemiyni
  56,91,Feselamun leke min ashabilyemiyni
  56,92,Ve emma in kane minelmukezzibiyneddalliyne
  56,93,Fenuzulun min hamiymin
  56,94,Ve tasliyetu cahÄḟymin
  56,95,ÄḞnne haza lehuve hakkulyakÄḟyni
  56,96,Fesebbih bismi rabbikelÂṀazÄḟymi